ernal processes. Above this\nscale, all spatially resolved galaxies have comparable SFMS slopes but exhibit\ntwo different behaviors, resulting likely from the rate of mass accretion at\nthe center of the galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2018 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
