possible to consider this algorithm for routine treatment\nplanning of RB patients, provided the limitations of the algorithm are known\nand taken into account by the medical physicist. Monte Carlo simulation is\nessential for knowing these limitations. Monte Carlo simulation is required for\noptimizing the treatment technique and the dedicated collimator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2018 18:51:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
