ntiferromagnetic models and cliques\nmaximize the partition function of ferromagnetic models.\n  These results settle a number of conjectures by Galvin-Tetali, Galvin, and\nCohen-Csikv\\'ari-Perkins-Tetali, and provide an alternate proof to a conjecture\nby Kahn.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2018 13:26:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2019 16:37:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 01:37:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-22"}
